headline: Camden Property Trust Issues Response to Department of Justice Lawsuit
summary: HOUSTON, January 08, 2025--Camden Property Trust (NYSE:CPT) disagrees with the allegations made in the amended complaint against RealPage, which added Camden and others as defendants. Camden will vigorously defend itself against these claims and intends to move for dismissal.
